Project description:

Files:

cepik_connector.py - is a script to get data from API - https://api.cepik.gov.pl
main.py - is a script to create a dash



Data period:
2019-09-01 - 2019-12-31

You can change the date in following lines:
data_start = "20190901"
data_end = "20191231"

Data (columns) which are getting from API:
- branch - "marka",
- model - "model",
- vehicle type - "rodzaj-pojazdu",
- vehicle body - "podrodzaj-pojazdu",
- vehicle orgin - "pochodzenie-pojazdu",
- production method - "sposob-produkcji"-,
- year of production - "rok-produkcji",
- date of first registration in country - "data-pierwszej-rejestracji-w-kraju",
- date of registration abroad - "data-rejestracji-za-granica",
- engine capacity - "pojemnosc-skokowa-silnika",
- engine power (HP) - "moc-netto-silnika",
- weight -  "masa-wlasna",
- number of seats - "liczba-miejsc-ogolem",
- fuel type - "rodzaj-paliwa",
- right-hand drive - "kierownica-po-prawej-stronie",
- voivodeship - "rejestracja-wojewodztwo"

To launch a dash you need to do execute this line in terminal:
streamlit run main.py
